Resume Screening Agent

The Resume Screening Agent is an AI-powered evaluation tool that analyzes how well a candidate's resume aligns with a given job description. It provides a structured, objective assessment designed to support HR teams, recruiters, and automated hiring workflows.

What the Agent Provides

Match Score (0–100)

Short alignment summary

Key strengths extracted from the resume

Identified gaps or risks

Final recommendation:
Strong Fit, Possible Fit, or Not a Fit


Evaluation Criteria (Weighted)

1. Skills & Tools Match
Required technologies
Nice-to-have skills

2. Experience Relevance
Similar roles and responsibilities
Domain experience
Project impact and achievements



3. Seniority Level Fit
Years of experience
Project complexity
Leadership or ownership roles



4. Education & Certifications
Considered only if important to the job posting

5. Additional Requirements
Location
Work authorization
Language
Time zone
Any role-specific constraints



Scoring Scale

Score Range	Interpretation
85–100	⭐ Strong Fit
70–84	⚠ Possible Fit
Below 70	❌ Not a Fit




